        askGeo - - true if you want to be asked if you want to manually input cowardinates on google fail Intended collum structure USDOT,_LEGAL_NAME_,_DBA_NAME_,_CARRIER_OPERATION_,_HM_FLAG_,_PC_FLAG_,_PHY_STREET_,_PHY_CITY_,_PHY_STATE_,_PHY_ZIP_,_PHY_COUNTRY_,_MAILING_STREET_,_MAILING_CITY_,_MAILING_STATE_,_MAILING_ZIP_,_MAILING_COUNTRY_,_TELEPHONE_,_FAX_,_EMAIL_ADDRESS_,_MCS150_DATE_,_MCS150_MILEAGE_,_MCS150_MILEAGE_YEAR_,_ADD_DATE_,_OIC_STATE_,_NBR_POWER_UNIT_,_DRIVER_TOTAL_ dates are to be input'd as [DD/MM/YYYY]
